      <li>A bird or animal nest blocking the chimney pot — common in properties used intermittently</li>
      <li>Slow draw or a fire that won't sustain — debris in the flue restricting airflow</li>
      <li>A fireplace in a weekender that gets lit hard for a few days then left</li>
    </ul>
