      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;Permanent resident and use the fireplace every night through winter. David found creosote build-up in the flue and a cracked liner tile. Very glad we had it inspected properly — will be booking annually.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">David K., Mornington</p></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;Heritage home near the old Mornington town centre. David worked carefully around the original fireplace and gave a thorough inspection. Very professional and good value.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Patricia W., Mornington</p></div>
    </div>
